notes.text: This advisory aggregates security fixes for the kernel SRPM in CIQ LTS for Rocky Linux 9.2. It addresses 15 CVEs: CVE-2022-50087, CVE-2023-0597, CVE-2025-38449, CVE-2025-38200, CVE-2025-38461, and 10 more.
